  <brief_title>Biomarkers of Bone Resorption in Metastatic Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Measurement of Biomarkers of Bone Resorption in Patients With Hormone Sensitive Bone Metastases From Prostate Cancer Treated With Antiandrogen Therapy and Bisphosphonates</official_title>
  <sponsors>
